ACCFOLDR.PRG is a Falcon only utliity which allows you to load your accessories
from a folder. Simply copy ACCFOLDR.PRG into your AUTO folder and place all
your accessories in a folder called ACCS on your boot drive.  

This is the first accessory redirection utility ( That I know of) to be
completely clean. It only redirects access to accessories on boot up and
after a res change. Try copying files with an ACC extension from the root
directory of your boot drive with any other utility installed and you'll
see what I mean.

